	"description": "Kriptofolio app series - Part 3\nThe most important thing to focus on when starting to build a new app is\narchitecture. The biggest mistake you can make is to go with no architecture\nstyle at all.\n\nThe topic of architecture choice has been quite controversial for the Android\ncommunity in recent years. Even Google decided to get involved. In 2017 they\nproposed their own approach of standardized architecture by releasing Android\nArchitecture Components. It was intended to make developers’ lives eas",
